abstract: Oklahoma senior Lauren Chamberlain hits her 90th home run to tie NCAA career softball record set by UCLA star Stacey Nuveman in 2002.
lead_paragraph: The Oklahoma senior Lauren Chamberlain hit her 90th home run to tie the N.C.A.A. career softball record, which the U.C.L.A. star Stacey Nuveman set in 2002.
